            . I am a Policeman. I received them in charge.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Grant's Defence. I know nothing of this young man.</p>
               <p>G. J. FORD re-examined. They were all three abreast in Hatton-garden, and when I felt them at me Green was exactly behind me - he turned round, and ran.</p>
